{"tid":1067562,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"到底有幾多人唔知頂你個肺係粗口？","createTime":"2019-03-18T14:57:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T16:18:55.000Z","uid":7186,"like":4,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f09cf466bc3c852e9d9089cc13cf71347cfb0b59","tid":1067562,"uid":7186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T14:57:21.000Z","msg":"以前聽中文老師講，頂你個肺都係源於性行為。<br />\n內容大概係話：<br />\n古時一個女人洞房時驚比人發現唔係處女，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是諗住整啲顏料扮係處女血，<br />\n點知唔小心倒咗啲藍色顏料出嚟，<br />\n嚇撚死人，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是就話係老公太勁頂到我個肺，<br />\n肺汁都出埋嚟。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前睇達哥台見好多小學雞話頂你個肺唔係粗口，冇性行為。<br />\n雖然唔覺得講粗口有問題，達哥講粗口好撚好笑，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都唔可以否認頂你個肺係粗口依個事實。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a477582751c722532b9c0d0c67f1a5fd3156f94f","tid":1067562,"uid":5793,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T14:59:22.000Z","msg":"頂你個肺都得，咁Pu你呀嬤都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f4fb30479306ac32a6894fb769abc798e25256","tid":1067562,"uid":136186,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:00:47.000Z","msg":"源於性行為就係粗口?<br />\n懷孕夠係源於性行為咁係咪粗口"},{"pid":"8a54567d22b5b18264ef708d4e4bdd7f5aa1092e","tid":1067562,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:03:35.000Z","msg":"原來以前啲人鳩噏下就變左係粗口<br />\n咁我而家話好強性能力強到仆街<br />\n30 年後都係粗口"},{"pid":"cfd1afbeb0456eccabac97d84f3721fc9336f0d1","tid":1067562,"uid":55458,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:05:30.000Z","msg":"插你個胃<br />\n㩒你個肚臍機關掣"},{"pid":"dee4dcfbe18cd5b909ea923b0ed83260a13f668f","tid":1067562,"uid":80176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-18T15:08:45.000Z","msg":"性交=粗口"},{"pid":"929